<br>
-Building, developing and maintaining a client base<br>
<br>
-Contacting customers via phone for promotions and other store-wide events<br>
<br>
-Providing superior customer service<br>
<br>
-Maintaining minimum selling productivity standards in home department<br>
<br>
-Promoting and acquiring new Neiman Marcus credit accounts<br>
<br>
-Performs additional tasks as required by Manager or Organization.<br>
